Notes on the prior_artifacts/ directory:

The prior_artifacts directory contains the author's previously published
work (Medium article PDF, NLP Evaluation portfolio HTML report, companion
HTML report) included verbatim under the author's own copyright. These
are reproduced here to document the prospective theoretical commitment
that predates the current empirical extension.

Notes on the Reddit corpus:

The corpus is collected from public Reddit posts and comments via Arctic
Shift, an academic Reddit preservation project. Usernames are not
retained. The corpus is redistributed for research reproducibility under
non-commercial fair-use research-purpose conventions documented in
Proferes et al. (2021) and Fiesler et al. (2020). Users wishing to
reproduce the corpus de novo can do so using the scraper code provided
in src/, subject to current Arctic Shift access terms.
